//000000000000a:40:{s:2:"id";s:5:"28634";s:4:"body";s:258:"甲买了3支签字笔、7支圆珠笔和1支铅笔，共花了32元，乙买了4支同样的签字笔、10支圆珠笔和1支铅笔，共花了43元。如果同样的签字笔、圆珠笔、铅笔各买一支，共用多少钱?（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）";s:7:"bd_desc";s:0:"";s:7:"options";s:113:"[{"cs":"A ", "text":"21元"},{"cs":"B ", "text":"11元"},{"cs":"C ", "text":"10元"},{"cs":"D ", "text":"17元"}]";s:11:"description";s:1102:"解法一：设签字笔每支x元，圆珠笔每支y元，铅笔每支z元，则可得&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/fc92e8f6b223a218de3d9b19bea6debd_0.png" /> ，（1）×3－（2）×2＝x＋y＋z=10（元）。因此，本题答案选择C选项。解法二：设签字笔每支x元，圆珠笔每支y元，铅笔每支z元，则可得&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/d48162dcbc4e777fd78b879b7f471a0f_1.png" />，假设y为已知量，则可解得&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/3572268e37990a06c5b6e2891144ae69_2.png" />，因此&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/26dd8db5453e9e5fb4b7105dd2748bf9_3.png" /> 。因此，本题答案选择C选项。解法三：设签字笔每支x元，圆珠笔每支y元，铅笔每支z元，则可得&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/d48162dcbc4e777fd78b879b7f471a0f_1.png" />。因为只有2个方程，3个未知数，肯定无法求解出所有的未知数，因此我们不妨假设y＝0，然后可求出&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/691ac7785fb90118d44295d6b79536d3_5.png" /> ，x＋y＋z=10。因此，答案选择C选项。";s:7:"dp_desc";s:233:"fc92e8f6b223a218de3d9b19bea6debd_0.png|d48162dcbc4e777fd78b879b7f471a0f_1.png|3572268e37990a06c5b6e2891144ae69_2.png|26dd8db5453e9e5fb4b7105dd2748bf9_3.png|d48162dcbc4e777fd78b879b7f471a0f_4.png|691ac7785fb90118d44295d6b79536d3_5.png";s:6:"answer";s:1:"C";s:8:"wrongans";s:1:"B";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:10:"optiontype";s:1:"1";s:8:"bigtype1";s:12:"数量关系";s:10:"smalltype1";s:12:"数学运算";s:10:"pointtype1";s:15:"不定方程组";s:5:"tagid";s:1:"0";s:6:"chance";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismock";s:1:"1";s:5:"qyear";s:4:"2009";s:5:"views";s:1:"2";s:6:"rorate";s:3:"250";s:7:"usetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"materialid";s:1:"0";s:4:"diff";s:1:"0";s:7:"addtime";s:1:"0";s:10:"updatetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"supplierid";s:1:"2";s:8:"sourceid";s:5:"55292";s:8:"insertid";s:1:"0";s:6:"extend";s:166:"<p class="item-p">解法一和解法二的计算量都较大，在考场中，时间非常紧张，因此可以采用第三种解法，快速得出正确选项。</p>";s:5:"skill";s:46:"<p class="item-p">整体消去、赋值法</p>";s:7:"bigtype";s:1:"2";s:9:"smalltype";s:2:"